---
description: Generated contract, tracer, protobuf, and binding boundaries
globs:
  - "crates/contracts/**"
  - "crates/sim/tracer/**"
  - "crates/bindings/fastlz/**"
  - ".gitmodules"
---

- Edit Solidity sources under `contracts/*/src`, not generated `contracts/out/**` artifacts.
- CI uses Foundry `v1.5.0` and recursive submodules for account-abstraction sources.
- The sim tracer is TypeScript built with Yarn through `crates/sim/build.rs`.
- FastLZ Rust bindings are generated from C/header inputs into Cargo `OUT_DIR`.
- Initialize submodules before drawing conclusions from missing contract or spec-test files.

Full details: `.agents/skills/contracts-generated/`.

